                              Command : PLAYERS

NAME
   players - List players currently connected to the game

Level: Expert

SYNTAX
   [##:##] Command : players

   [##:##] Command : players

   Fri Sep 29 17:27:42 1995
               #                                   time  idle last command
   Khazad'ur  34             tetherow@nol.nol.org  0:38   32s cen 0,0
   children    0    children@RedDragon.Empire.Net  0:16    7s play
   2 players

#  the country number of the player.
time  the total number of hours:minutes the player has been connected today
idle  the number of seconds since the player has typed their last command
last command  the last command that the player typed

If you are not a deity and the BLITZ option is off, then the "players" command
will only list your allies (and omit userid@host.name).

SEE ALSO
   country, Nations, Communication, Deity, Playing

